{
  "page": "Selhorys",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2;\">Selhorys</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nTown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> region, <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Government</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Triarchs_of_Volantis\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Triarchs of Volantis\">Triarchs of Volantis</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Free_Cities.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Selhorys is located in Free Cities\"><img alt=\"Selhorys is located in Free Cities\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/300px-Free_Cities.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/450px-Free_Cities.png 1.5x, /images/a/a3/Free_Cities.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 78.3%; left: 70.8%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Selhorys\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Selhorys</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and the location of Selhorys\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Selhorys</b> is a walled <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a> town located at the confluence of the <a href=\"/index.php/Selhoru\" title=\"Selhoru\">Selhoru</a> and the lower <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a> in western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It lies north of <a href=\"/index.php/Valysar\" title=\"Valysar\">Valysar</a>, northwest of <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a>, and south of <a href=\"/index.php/Chroyane\" title=\"Chroyane\">Chroyane</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Layout\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Layout</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Chapters_that_take_place_at_Selhorys\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapters that take place at Selhorys</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Layout\">Layout</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Selhorys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Layout\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Although it is larger than the cities of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Selhorys is still considered a town, not an independent city.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Alone among the major towns, Selhorys stands upon the eastern bank of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a>, making it more vulnerable to <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> than its sister towns west of the river.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Timber from the <a href=\"/index.php/Forest_of_Qohor\" title=\"Forest of Qohor\">Forest of Qohor</a> is sold in the markets of Selhorys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_qohor.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_qohor.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Selhorys has towers, domes, and cobbled paths. The city's sandstone walls shelter shops, stalls, and storehouses along the piers. The river gate is guarded by <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a> slave soldiers with tiger stripes, while <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitution\" title=\"Prostitution\">prostitutes</a> in its brothels are also slaves. Volantene river galleys loaded with slave soldiers protect the waterway.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Lanterns within the city are made of colored glass, unlike the parchment lanterns outside of the city walls.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>The main square in Selhorys contains an ornate but headless statue of <a href=\"/index.php/Triarch\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Triarch\">Triarch</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Horonno\" title=\"Horonno\">Horonno</a> and a stone <a href=\"/index.php/Red_temple\" title=\"Red temple\">red temple</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Pleasure_house\" title=\"Pleasure house\">Pleasure houses</a> and inns front the square, including a large stone inn with an <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Men_of_the_River\" title=\"Old Men of the River\">immense turtle</a> hanging above its door.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Selhorys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:307px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dockside_Brothel_by_Yoann_BoissonnetII.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/Dockside_Brothel_by_Yoann_BoissonnetII.png/305px-Dockside_Brothel_by_Yoann_BoissonnetII.png\" width=\"305\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/Dockside_Brothel_by_Yoann_BoissonnetII.png/458px-Dockside_Brothel_by_Yoann_BoissonnetII.png 1.5x, /images/2/2b/Dockside_Brothel_by_Yoann_BoissonnetII.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Dockside_Brothel_by_Yoann_BoissonnetII.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Dockside Brothel in Selhorys - by Yoann Boissonnet ©</div></div></div>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Spice_War\" title=\"Second Spice War\">Second Spice War</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Garin_the_Great\" title=\"Garin the Great\">Garin the Great</a> achieved his first victory over the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a> at Selhorys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The town has been under the authority of <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> since the <a href=\"/index.php/Century_of_Blood\" title=\"Century of Blood\">Century of Blood</a>, the years of expansion under the <a href=\"/index.php/Tigers_(Volantis)\" title=\"Tigers (Volantis)\">tigers</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Selhorys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Selhorys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>A <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkish</a> envoy comes to Selhorys with chests of gold and gems and two hundred slaves, seeking support for their war against <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>   \n</p><p>The <i><a href=\"/index.php/Shy_Maid\" title=\"Shy Maid\">Shy Maid</a></i> stops at Selhorys, and <a href=\"/index.php/Haldon_Halfmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Haldon Halfmaester\">Haldon Halfmaester</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> listen to a <a href=\"/index.php/Red_priest\" title=\"Red priest\">red priest</a> calling for <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> to support <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>. Tyrion plays <i><a href=\"/index.php/Cyvasse\" title=\"Cyvasse\">cyvasse</a></i> with <a href=\"/index.php/Qavo_Nogarys\" title=\"Qavo Nogarys\">Qavo Nogarys</a>, a customs officer, within the stone inn. After fornicating with the <a href=\"/index.php/Sunset_girl\" title=\"Sunset girl\">sunset girl</a> at a modest brothel, Tyrion is kidnapped by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and taken by him to <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> on horseback.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Selhorys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Shops and stalls and storehouses huddled beneath a sandstone wall. The towers and domes of the city were visible beyond it, reddened by the light of the setting sun. No, not a city. Selhorys was still accounted a mere town, and was ruled from <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Old Volantis</a>. This was not <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapters_that_take_place_at_Selhorys\">Chapters that take place at Selhorys</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Selhorys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Chapters that take place at Selhorys\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_22\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 22\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i>: 22. Tyrion VI</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Selhorys&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiafthe_free_cities.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>, The Free Cities.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href